<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ فِي الْحَدِيثِ:</span> <span class="c2">« فَإِنَّ اللهَ <span class="special">﷿</span> قَضَى عَلَى لِسَانِ نَبِيِّهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: سَمِعَ اللهُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَهُ »</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>